@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US 2.2.10 – View the Status of Vessel Visit Notifications\nSystem Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber
actor "Shipping Agent Representative" as Agent
participant ":System" as System

activate Agent

'--- View All Notifications ---
Agent -> System : 1: Request list of all Vessel Visit Notifications\n(submitted by self or same organization)
activate System
System --> Agent : 1.1: Return notifications with status,\ndock (if approved), and rejection reason (if rejected)
deactivate System

'--- Apply Filters ---
Agent -> System : 2: Apply filters (vessel, status,\nrepresentative, date range)
activate System
System --> Agent : 2.1: Return filtered list of matching notifications
deactivate System

deactivate Agent
@enduml
